1
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:48,009
[Fangs of Fortune]

2
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:51,060
[Episode 20]

3
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,430
Jiu?

4
00:02:06,130 --> 00:02:06,910
Jiu?

5
00:02:21,050 --> 00:02:22,100
Sister Pei!

6
00:02:23,230 --> 00:02:24,260
Sister Pei.

7
00:02:27,270 --> 00:02:28,190
Sister Pei.

8
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:31,440
Don't kill her.

9
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,820
You really care about her, don't you?

10
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:35,100
I just don't think

11
00:02:36,780 --> 00:02:38,460
you should alert them.

12
00:02:43,090 --> 00:02:43,880
After all,

13
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:48,000
our target is Zhao Yuanzhou.

14
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:49,850
I'll wait for it to dry.

15
00:02:54,170 --> 00:02:55,410
Just a small patch is wet.

16
00:02:55,410 --> 00:02:56,610
Why bother?

17
00:03:00,530 --> 00:03:01,550
Bai Jiu,

18
00:03:02,550 --> 00:03:04,530
we need to check your wrist.

19
00:03:35,660 --> 00:03:37,610
I am indeed from Chongwu Camp.

20
00:03:45,350 --> 00:03:47,530
You're very curious, aren't you?

21
00:03:49,030 --> 00:03:50,800
Yes, I am.

22
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:55,230
When did he start to seal my five senses?

23
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:00,690
You each take one.

24
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:03,600
I made these detoxification pills myself.

25
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:04,840
Taste.

26
00:04:11,330 --> 00:04:12,630
What do you want from me?

27
00:04:12,630 --> 00:04:14,450
This is the new version of Huanling Powder I developed.

28
00:04:14,450 --> 00:04:15,530
Are you ready?

29
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:19,360
Smell.

30
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,610
I feel nothing.

31
00:04:22,890 --> 00:04:24,800
I even want to laugh.

32
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:30,230
I'm so scared.

33
00:04:30,590 --> 00:04:32,010
Sight.

34
00:04:32,090 --> 00:04:34,130
Then why are you covering my eyes?

35
00:04:34,190 --> 00:04:35,790
Cover your own eyes.

36
00:04:36,750 --> 00:04:38,180
I can't see the road.

37
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,150
It's so scary.

38
00:04:39,170 --> 00:04:40,270
What's that sound?

39
00:04:40,290 --> 00:04:41,590
Put this on.

40
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:44,190
I think something is definitely wrong with this voice.

41
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:45,130
Don't listen.

42
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:46,450
Hearing.

43
00:04:52,890 --> 00:04:56,130
I never expected that seemingly harmless Little Bunny

44
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:59,090
could be so meticulous.

45
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,360
To accomplish great things,

46
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:03,520
one must not only have good foresight

47
00:05:04,710 --> 00:05:06,420
but also patience

48
00:05:07,570 --> 00:05:09,490
to set up the game step by step.

49
00:05:10,220 --> 00:05:11,530
Zhao Yuanzhou,

50
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:15,440
from the moment you entered Tiandu City,

51
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:17,720
you have been stepping into this chessboard,

52
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,670
bit by bit.

53
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:23,280
Where do you think the list of these five people

54
00:05:23,350 --> 00:05:25,080
in the vanguard squad formed by

55
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:28,280
the Demon Hunting Bureau came from?

56
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,170
Didn't Mr. Zhuo make it?

57
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:36,470
So it was you.

58
00:05:38,860 --> 00:05:40,840
To obtain your inner core,

59
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:43,360
we must seal your five senses.

60
00:05:44,580 --> 00:05:47,300
Bai Jiu could do that for me.

61
00:05:47,909 --> 00:05:49,950
However, he lacks experience

62
00:05:50,409 --> 00:05:52,980
and needs someone to protect him.

63
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:55,360
Ms. Pei,

64
00:05:56,650 --> 00:05:58,390
you don't think our Chongwu Camp

65
00:05:58,390 --> 00:05:59,790
is a place you can enter

66
00:05:59,790 --> 00:06:01,600
or exit at will, do you?

67
00:06:02,030 --> 00:06:05,090
You deliberately arranged for me to leave Chongwu Camp

68
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:07,630
and then be noticed by the Demon Hunting Bureau.

69
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:10,040
Ms. Pei, not only are you a good archer,

70
00:06:10,430 --> 00:06:13,360
but you are also the bodyguard of the Prime Minister.

71
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:16,360
Moreover, you have a grudge against Chongwu Camp.

72
00:06:16,710 --> 00:06:17,800
Who else would

73
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,650
the Demon Hunting Bureau choose

74
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:22,840
besides an outstanding talent like you?

75
00:06:24,470 --> 00:06:27,870
Besides, you just suffered the loss of your younger brother.

76
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:29,590
When facing Bai Jiu,

77
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:32,720
would there be any emotional projection?

78
00:06:32,770 --> 00:06:34,850
Over time, when you grow deep feelings for him,

79
00:06:34,850 --> 00:06:37,380
you will surely risk your life to protect him.

80
00:06:38,460 --> 00:06:41,590
Bai Jiu calls you "Sister Pei" every day;

81
00:06:43,650 --> 00:06:45,510
you must be enjoying that, right?

82
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:47,550
Despicable.

83
00:06:48,310 --> 00:06:50,400
If Bai Jiu couldn't succeed,

84
00:06:51,270 --> 00:06:53,070
I would still have a backup plan.

85
00:06:55,550 --> 00:06:57,400
Even Mr. Zhuo

86
00:06:58,830 --> 00:07:01,240
is one of your pawns.

87
00:07:02,730 --> 00:07:05,350
Zhuo Yichen is the leader of the Demon Hunting Bureau.

88
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:08,280
It was reasonable for him to join the vanguard squad.

89
00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:11,080
Besides, he has the Cloud Light Sword.

90
00:07:11,110 --> 00:07:13,510
He's the only one who can kill you.

91
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:16,440
As for Baize Goddess...

92
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:18,560
I'll cooperate with Li Lun

93
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,550
to help him destroy the Baize Token.

94
00:07:20,550 --> 00:07:22,270
I promise I'll give you

95
00:07:22,970 --> 00:07:24,570
Zhao Yuanzhou's inner core.

96
00:07:27,140 --> 00:07:29,300
What about your promise to me?

97
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:31,070
To merge

98
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:33,550
the Baize Token hidden in you and Wen Xiao,

99
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:36,110
we naturally need to bind you together

100
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,710
to endure hardships

101
00:07:38,150 --> 00:07:40,280
so that you can understand each other.

102
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:44,110
Now, there's only one last step left

103
00:07:44,110 --> 00:07:45,510
to seal your five senses.

104
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:49,120
I just need to use a silver needle

105
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:51,550
to seal your touch,

106
00:07:53,110 --> 00:07:55,240
and everything will be accomplished.

107
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:01,290
What does a mortal like you

108
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:04,430
want with my inner core?

109
00:08:04,590 --> 00:08:06,700
Who wants your foul inner core?

110
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:09,160
From the beginning,

111
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:11,620
what I want is always the Ever-Burning Wood.

112
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,500
It's been such a hard journey.

113
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:16,910
I finally found

114
00:08:16,910 --> 00:08:18,070
the Ever-Burning Wood that he wants.

115
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:19,190
It is said that

116
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,930
this is the last piece of Ever-Burning Wood in the world.

117
00:08:21,930 --> 00:08:23,660
We must keep a close watch on it.

118
00:08:26,370 --> 00:08:27,530
Eight years ago,

119
00:08:28,180 --> 00:08:30,390
you inhaled

120
00:08:30,730 --> 00:08:33,430
the last piece of Ever-Burning Wood that I had found

121
00:08:33,430 --> 00:08:34,760
with great difficulty.

122
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:39,620
I have been looking for you for eight years.

123
00:08:57,090 --> 00:08:58,350
Go ahead, my disciple.

124
00:09:22,150 --> 00:09:23,020
Bai Jiu,

125
00:09:24,540 --> 00:09:26,510
aren't we your friends?

126
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,220
Don't come any closer.

127
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,790
I don't want to hurt you.

128
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:48,430
You've already said so much;

129
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:51,190
how could I possibly

130
00:09:51,190 --> 00:09:53,520
just let Little Bunny stick a needle in me?

131
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:18,040
What's wrong, Zhao Yuanzhou?

132
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:22,810
It seems like you can't cast your spells.

133
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,410
Jiu,

134
00:10:41,230 --> 00:10:42,440
think it through.

135
00:11:22,770 --> 00:11:23,580
Stop.

136
00:12:07,010 --> 00:12:16,190
[Book of Rites]

137
00:12:20,110 --> 00:12:22,170
As expected, at the critical moment,

138
00:12:23,450 --> 00:12:25,180
you still wished for him to live

139
00:12:26,740 --> 00:12:28,200
and didn't want him to die.

140
00:12:33,590 --> 00:12:34,350
Don't worry.

141
00:12:34,830 --> 00:12:36,440
Whether it's Mr. Fan's order

142
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:38,650
or the Prime Minister's,

143
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,620
it cannot suppress me.

144
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,610
The only one who can kill Zhao Yuanzhou

145
00:12:45,710 --> 00:12:47,060
is me.

146
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:51,550
I won't be anyone's executioner.

147
00:12:52,710 --> 00:12:54,030
Well, if we

148
00:12:54,610 --> 00:12:56,280
restore the Baize Token

149
00:12:57,310 --> 00:13:01,310
and are ultimately able to suppress Zhao Yuanzhou's malicious energy,

150
00:13:01,340 --> 00:13:02,680
will you still kill him?

151
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,730
The Yao Water was polluted,

152
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,860
and the Divine Wood went missing.

153
00:13:12,640 --> 00:13:14,160
The "if" you mentioned

154
00:13:14,460 --> 00:13:16,120
seems too distant to hope for.

155
00:13:16,910 --> 00:13:19,440
I won't answer such a hopeless hypothetical.

156
00:13:20,010 --> 00:13:21,120
But what if

157
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:23,560
the hope is not distant?

158
00:13:25,690 --> 00:13:26,790
What do you mean?

159
00:13:27,270 --> 00:13:29,220
Zhao Yuanzhou once mentioned to me

160
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:32,000
that the clues about the Divine Wood

161
00:13:32,350 --> 00:13:33,610
are in Situ's Mansion.

162
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:36,290
Situ's Mansion?

163
00:13:37,070 --> 00:13:37,960
Mr. Zhuo.

164
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:43,580
Mr. Situ Ming.

165
00:13:43,620 --> 00:13:44,640
Mr. Zhuo,

166
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:47,310
please take Ms. Wen Xiao away through the back door now.

167
00:13:47,310 --> 00:13:49,470
Mr. Situ, why are you so panicked?

168
00:13:49,670 --> 00:13:50,950
What happened?

169
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:07,910
Zhen Mei,

170
00:14:07,930 --> 00:14:09,090
what are you doing?

171
00:14:12,270 --> 00:14:14,360
Wen Xiao from the Demon Hunting Bureau

172
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:16,090
murdered the Prime Minister,

173
00:14:16,810 --> 00:14:18,400
resisted arrest, and fled,

174
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:20,010
committing a grave crime.

175
00:14:21,110 --> 00:14:23,460
Chongwu Camp has been ordered to capture her.

176
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:25,590
Those who block the way will be killed.

177
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:27,110
The Prime Minister was murdered.

178
00:14:27,110 --> 00:14:28,870
Chongwu Camp is here to arrest the criminal.

179
00:14:28,870 --> 00:14:30,670
They claimed the murderer is...

180
00:14:32,750 --> 00:14:34,290
is Ms. Wen Xiao.

181
00:14:34,950 --> 00:14:36,270
Utterly absurd!

182
00:14:36,310 --> 00:14:38,170
How could it possibly be Wen Xiao?

183
00:14:38,300 --> 00:14:40,860
Many of the Prime Minister's attendants

184
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:44,380
witnessed Wen Xiao publicly stop the horse.

185
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:51,270
They said that after Wen Xiao got into the carriage,

186
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:52,930
she brutally killed the Prime Minister.

187
00:14:52,930 --> 00:14:54,590
The blood dripped all the way.

188
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:59,210
All the servants saw with their own eyes

189
00:14:59,560 --> 00:15:00,870
that inside the carriage,

190
00:15:00,060 --> 00:15:03,200
[Book of Rites]

191
00:15:01,180 --> 00:15:03,410
the Prime Minister's body was mutilated.

192
00:15:03,410 --> 00:15:05,160
Wen Xiao was covered in blood

193
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,960
and ran away.

194
00:15:10,470 --> 00:15:11,600
Nonsense!

195
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:13,360
Wen Xiao was in the Demon Hunting Bureau all night.

196
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:15,290
All the guards can testify to that.

197
00:15:15,330 --> 00:15:17,170
I was here all night,

198
00:15:17,830 --> 00:15:20,430
being punished with house arrest by my father.

199
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:21,770
Chongwu Camp

200
00:15:22,050 --> 00:15:23,740
is clearly framing me.

201
00:15:23,770 --> 00:15:24,650
In such a serious event

202
00:15:24,650 --> 00:15:25,790
as the Prime Minister's murder,

203
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:27,850
they wouldn't casually frame anyone

204
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:30,360
unless they were absolutely confident.

205
00:15:30,710 --> 00:15:31,590
There must be

206
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:33,380
something fishy going on.

207
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,910
The situation is unclear now,

208
00:15:35,910 --> 00:15:37,790
and there are a bunch of witnesses on both sides.

209
00:15:37,790 --> 00:15:39,520
We cannot prove our innocence.

210
00:15:39,550 --> 00:15:40,350
Mr. Zhuo,

211
00:15:40,580 --> 00:15:42,950
you should take Ms. Wen Xiao and leave now.

212
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:46,470
Before Chongwu Camp closes the city gates,

213
00:15:46,470 --> 00:15:48,680
I'll take Wen Xiao and leave the city as soon as possible.

214
00:15:48,680 --> 00:15:49,390
No.

215
00:15:49,810 --> 00:15:51,210
I'm not leaving the city.

216
00:15:51,710 --> 00:15:53,370
They think I will escape.

217
00:15:54,770 --> 00:15:56,790
So, at this moment, Tiandu City

218
00:15:57,060 --> 00:15:58,700
is the safest place.

219
00:15:59,420 --> 00:16:00,750
That's true.

220
00:16:00,910 --> 00:16:02,770
But Tiandu City is not that large.

221
00:16:02,830 --> 00:16:04,710
Chongwu Camp has ample forces in Tiandu City.

222
00:16:04,710 --> 00:16:06,730
They could search the entire city in two or three days.

223
00:16:06,730 --> 00:16:07,910
By the time they realize...

224
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:08,470
So,

225
00:16:08,890 --> 00:16:10,730
Mr. Situ, please shelter me.

226
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:12,880
What?

227
00:16:16,110 --> 00:16:17,310
Urgent matters need flexible solutions.

228
00:16:17,310 --> 00:16:18,310
It's not up to you.

229
00:16:19,790 --> 00:16:21,390
I'd like to see

230
00:16:22,070 --> 00:16:23,660
who dares to stop me.

231
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:24,960
I do.

232
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:45,550
[Arrest Warrant]

233
00:16:41,550 --> 00:16:43,510
King Xiang has issued an urgent decree

234
00:16:43,510 --> 00:16:47,440
to capture the true murderer, Wen Xiao, who killed the Prime Minister.

235
00:16:47,950 --> 00:16:50,220
Anyone who dares to obstruct will be regarded

236
00:16:50,220 --> 00:16:52,220
as having committed the same crime.

237
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:56,320
Go in and arrest her.

238
00:17:31,990 --> 00:17:33,280
Commander,

239
00:17:33,430 --> 00:17:34,700
we have searched the entire Demon Hunting Bureau

240
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:35,960
and haven't found her.

241
00:17:39,750 --> 00:17:41,610
Close the city gate immediately.

242
00:17:41,810 --> 00:17:43,470
and launch a citywide search.

243
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:45,940
Inspect all inns and taverns,

244
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:49,710
and issue a wanted notice

245
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:52,760
for the serious criminal, Wen Xiao.

246
00:18:21,120 --> 00:18:22,050
Come out.

247
00:18:26,710 --> 00:18:27,350
Let's go.

248
00:18:27,350 --> 00:18:28,160
Go inside.

249
00:18:34,410 --> 00:18:36,940
Mr. Situ, I never expected your home to have such a rustic charm.

250
00:18:36,940 --> 00:18:37,850
Hurry inside.

251
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:39,280
Don't let others see you.

252
00:18:44,930 --> 00:18:45,970
Come on.

253
00:19:02,100 --> 00:19:03,700
What's wrong with that room?

254
00:19:04,110 --> 00:19:05,560
Why is it sealed?

255
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:08,350
Oh.

256
00:19:08,550 --> 00:19:10,400
That's my wife's bedroom.

257
00:19:10,510 --> 00:19:12,300
She has been bedridden for many years because of her illness

258
00:19:12,300 --> 00:19:13,520
and is sensitive to light and wind.

259
00:19:13,520 --> 00:19:15,250
It has been like this for years.

260
00:19:17,220 --> 00:19:18,040
Ms. Wen Xiao,

261
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:18,590
come.

262
00:19:18,610 --> 00:19:19,330
Follow me.

263
00:19:19,950 --> 00:19:20,390
Okay.

264
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:45,550
Jiu hasn't been home for a long time.

265
00:19:45,550 --> 00:19:47,610
How about you stay in his room for now?

266
00:20:23,110 --> 00:20:23,980
What a coincidence.

267
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:25,030
You're here too?

268
00:20:26,330 --> 00:20:27,550
You're here too?

269
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:38,180
I didn't expect

270
00:20:39,290 --> 00:20:40,380
it was Bai Jiu.

271
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:42,110
Yeah,

272
00:20:43,450 --> 00:20:45,310
I didn't expect it was him either.

273
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:47,210
I actually didn't expect you

274
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:49,470
to be hunted down across the entire city.

275
00:20:49,470 --> 00:20:50,590
Impressive.

276
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:53,110
What's so surprising about that?

277
00:20:53,370 --> 00:20:55,500
Since Mr. Situ is willing to take me in,

278
00:20:55,690 --> 00:20:59,400
I can take the chance to investigate the clues about the Divine Wood.

279
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:01,370
It's you guys who are weird.

280
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:03,550
Why are you here?

281
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:05,590
To find the Divine Wood, of course.

282
00:21:14,600 --> 00:21:15,520
