00:34:42,460 --> 00:34:45,170
I'm going out to find the best master to learn from.

571
00:34:45,170 --> 00:34:46,860
One day,

572
00:34:47,350 --> 00:34:48,989
I will definitely cure you.

573
00:35:44,790 --> 00:35:45,750
You are...

574
00:35:46,260 --> 00:35:48,420
I'm the new apprentice.

575
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:49,880
My name is...

576
00:35:50,040 --> 00:35:50,680
Si...

577
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:53,460
My name is Bai Jiu.

578
00:35:55,060 --> 00:35:55,910
Master,

579
00:35:55,940 --> 00:35:56,890
really?

580
00:35:56,930 --> 00:35:59,130
Can you really bring my mom back to life?

581
00:35:59,370 --> 00:36:00,950
I promise you

582
00:36:01,040 --> 00:36:02,900
I will bring your mom back to life.

583
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:05,760
But I need your help with something as well.

584
00:36:05,980 --> 00:36:08,910
Join the vanguard squad of the Demon Hunting Bureau.

585
00:36:09,220 --> 00:36:12,110
I just need you to seal Zhu Yan's five senses.

586
00:36:19,390 --> 00:36:20,940
I know you have a kind heart.

587
00:36:20,970 --> 00:36:22,660
But Zhu Yan is a demon.

588
00:36:22,680 --> 00:36:24,880
Your mother was killed by a demon.

589
00:36:25,060 --> 00:36:27,340
If he isn't eliminated,

590
00:36:27,740 --> 00:36:29,010
there will be

591
00:36:29,080 --> 00:36:30,640
more children like you

592
00:36:30,640 --> 00:36:31,970
who lost their mothers.

593
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:37,520
Jiu,

594
00:36:37,670 --> 00:36:39,240
you really are a fool.

595
00:36:39,310 --> 00:36:41,480
Your mother was not killed by a demon,

596
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:42,710
nor is she sick.

597
00:36:44,930 --> 00:36:46,730
You were deceived by Wen Zongyu.

598
00:36:48,720 --> 00:36:49,890
Then my mom is...

599
00:36:59,420 --> 00:37:00,650
Mr. Situ,

600
00:37:01,540 --> 00:37:03,400
don't hide it from Jiu any longer.

601
00:38:14,860 --> 00:38:15,720
Where is my mom?

602
00:38:21,750 --> 00:38:22,790
Where is my mom?

603
00:38:30,790 --> 00:38:32,090
This is your mom.

604
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:37,970
Nonsense.

605
00:38:39,200 --> 00:38:41,260
Your father is not talking nonsense.

606
00:38:41,960 --> 00:38:42,940
Your mother

607
00:38:45,250 --> 00:38:46,760
is not human.

608
00:38:49,670 --> 00:38:51,380
Your mother, like Ying Lei,

609
00:38:52,070 --> 00:38:53,980
is half god and half demon.

610
00:38:54,490 --> 00:38:56,320
She was born in ancient times.

611
00:38:57,260 --> 00:38:59,020
She's the same age as the gods.

612
00:39:03,290 --> 00:39:04,130
Yes.

613
00:39:04,310 --> 00:39:05,940
Your mother is the descendant of the White Emperor Shaohao

614
00:39:05,940 --> 00:39:07,960
and the Divine Tree of Jianmu.

615
00:39:11,190 --> 00:39:12,480
Her true form shares

616
00:39:12,500 --> 00:39:15,840
the same origin as the Divine Wood that transformed into the power of Baize,

617
00:39:15,840 --> 00:39:17,640
inheriting its spiritual vein.

618
00:39:17,910 --> 00:39:19,880
Therefore, during the Blood Moon eight years ago,

619
00:39:19,880 --> 00:39:21,390
the disappearance of the Baize Token

620
00:39:21,390 --> 00:39:22,790
severely injured her.

621
00:39:22,790 --> 00:39:23,280
Mom!

622
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:25,440
She was forced to manifest her true form.

623
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:27,520
Mom!

624
00:39:27,960 --> 00:39:30,040
Mom!

625
00:39:50,560 --> 00:39:52,530
Even if my mom turned into a tree

626
00:39:52,630 --> 00:39:54,290
and returned to her true form,

627
00:39:54,320 --> 00:39:56,650
why has she never talked to me

628
00:39:57,950 --> 00:39:59,480
or been willing to respond?

629
00:40:01,690 --> 00:40:03,420
With the loss of the Baize Token

630
00:40:04,850 --> 00:40:07,180
and the Goddess absent from her position,

631
00:40:07,530 --> 00:40:09,860
the Wilderness has fallen into disarray.

632
00:40:10,690 --> 00:40:13,300
Therefore, Lord Bai Yan lost her soul

633
00:40:13,900 --> 00:40:15,710
and had no choice but to stay in her true form

634
00:40:15,710 --> 00:40:17,390
in the world.

635
00:40:20,810 --> 00:40:21,680
Mom,

636
00:40:23,170 --> 00:40:24,360
can you hear me?

637
00:40:26,820 --> 00:40:27,430
I...

638
00:40:28,750 --> 00:40:30,270
I'm Jiu.

639
00:40:32,250 --> 00:40:33,390
I'm back.

640
00:40:40,960 --> 00:40:41,970
I'm back.

641
00:40:59,930 --> 00:41:02,410
Can my mom return to her original form?

642
00:41:03,490 --> 00:41:05,550
As long as the Baize Token is repaired

643
00:41:06,050 --> 00:41:07,850
and the Wilderness is restored,

644
00:41:08,970 --> 00:41:10,640
your mother will come back.

645
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:16,320
Why did no one tell me?

646
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:19,690
You were too young at that time.

647
00:41:20,120 --> 00:41:20,960
I didn't know

648
00:41:20,960 --> 00:41:22,090
how you would accept

649
00:41:22,380 --> 00:41:24,490
all of this after I told you.

650
00:41:26,080 --> 00:41:28,880
For an ordinary person, it's indeed hard to accept

651
00:41:29,120 --> 00:41:31,720
without going through all this.

652
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:34,690
But Bai Jiu has the right to know the truth.

653
00:41:36,780 --> 00:41:38,190
Although he is young,

654
00:41:38,610 --> 00:41:41,070
he is much more mature than children his age.

655
00:41:41,770 --> 00:41:42,940
I believe

656
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:45,360
that if you had told him

657
00:41:45,380 --> 00:41:46,660
the truth back then,

658
00:41:47,290 --> 00:41:48,850
Jiu would have understood.

659
00:41:50,030 --> 00:41:51,130
If you

660
00:41:51,240 --> 00:41:53,020
had told me the truth earlier,

661
00:41:54,290 --> 00:41:56,950
perhaps I wouldn't have been used by Wen Zongyu.

662
00:41:57,760 --> 00:41:59,250
I'm sorry.

663
00:41:59,270 --> 00:42:00,030
No.

664
00:42:00,880 --> 00:42:02,030
It was my fault.

665
00:42:04,490 --> 00:42:05,470
I'm sorry.

666
00:42:07,680 --> 00:42:08,850
I was wrong.

667
00:42:11,500 --> 00:42:12,600
I'm sorry.

668
00:42:14,130 --> 00:42:15,650
I hurt you guys.

669
00:42:17,290 --> 00:42:18,410
All of you

670
00:42:18,630 --> 00:42:19,960
have been sincere to me,

671
00:42:22,260 --> 00:42:24,140
but I have let down your trust.

672
00:42:25,500 --> 00:42:26,670
Jiu.

673
00:42:47,020 --> 00:42:48,130
Jiu,

674
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:50,200
you've grown up.

675
00:42:50,970 --> 00:42:52,520
The bond between father and son,

676
00:42:52,520 --> 00:42:54,180
the loyalty between friends,

677
00:42:54,570 --> 00:42:56,630
rights and wrongs, gains and losses—

678
00:42:58,320 --> 00:43:00,350
you can understand them on your own.

679
00:43:03,940 --> 00:43:05,470
It's okay to make mistakes.

680
00:43:07,530 --> 00:43:08,620
As long as

681
00:43:08,640 --> 00:43:10,810
you can bear the cost of growing up

682
00:43:12,140 --> 00:43:13,400
and try to make amends.

683
00:43:19,050 --> 00:43:20,850
The sea of suffering is endless.

684
00:43:21,660 --> 00:43:23,920
As long as you return to the shore in time,

685
00:43:24,330 --> 00:43:27,390
there will still be a brilliant sunset waiting for you.

686
00:43:35,760 --> 00:43:36,560
In fact,

687
00:43:37,120 --> 00:43:38,720
the real culprit

688
00:43:39,680 --> 00:43:40,960
is not you, this easily fooled

689
00:43:40,960 --> 00:43:42,260
Little Bunny.

690
00:43:42,660 --> 00:43:45,280
But the truly cunning and deceitful wolf.

691
00:43:48,440 --> 00:43:49,440
Stop hiding.

692
00:43:49,670 --> 00:43:51,000
Come out.

